---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import PageMasthead from '../components/PageMasthead.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="about — the keepers." description="What the keepers is, who runs it, how it stays free." current="about">

  <PageMasthead
    title="about us."
    eyebrow="who we are · why this exists"
    subscript="THE KEEPERS"
    cutouts={[]}
  />

  <div class="container container-narrow page">
    <p class="lead">
      One San Franciscan every Saturday. Someone holding a recipe, a routine, a room, a record, or a refusal the city would lose without them. Reader-funded. No parent company. No paywall. No AI bylines.
    </p>

    <h2>what we publish.</h2>
    <p>One profile a week, every saturday morning. Quarterly best of guides written by <em>named</em> editors. Reader-submitted hidden spots, vetted by the editor before they appear. Five personality quizzes that each end in a reading list. That's the whole publication.</p>

    <h2>how we stay free.</h2>
    <p>Readers fund the reporting. We don't run banner ads. We don't sell your data. We don't have a paywall. <em>Seventy-five</em> percent of every donated dollar pays student journalists and editors. <em>Twenty-five</em> percent goes to local bay area charities, named on the support page, audited annually.</p>

    <h2>five principles.</h2>
    <ol>
      <li><strong>Named bylines, <em>always</em>.</strong> Every word on this site is written by a named human. No AI bylines, no syndicated filler, no aggregated reposts.</li>
      <li><strong>One thing per <em>page</em>.</strong> The homepage curates. The article reads. The best of guides. We don't cross-breed.</li>
      <li><strong>Specificity over <em>abstraction</em>.</strong> Real names, real prices, real dates. The shop owner is a person, not a stand-in for "small business."</li>
      <li><strong>Editorial <em>firewall</em>.</strong> Sponsored entries are labeled. The list still has to meet the editorial bar. Sponsors do not pick stories.</li>
      <li><strong>Protect the <em>small</em>.</strong> If a place can't handle traffic, we describe it without naming it. Hidden spots are the proof.</li>
    </ol>

    <h2>who runs it.</h2>
    <p>Eric, founder and editor. Plus Nicholas and Daisy on the bylines. <a href="/team">Read the team page</a> for bios.</p>

    <h2>where the money goes.</h2>
    <p>Full revenue breakdown lives on the <a href="/support">support page</a>. Editorial standards on the <a href="/standards">standards page</a>. Public corrections log on the <a href="/corrections">corrections page</a>. If we get something wrong we say so.</p>

    <p class="about-cta">
      <a class="btn-ghost" href="/stories">read a saturday letter →</a>
      <a class="btn-jumbo" href="/support">become a supporter →</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page { padding-block: var(--s-9); }
  .page h1 { margin-block: var(--s-3) var(--s-5); }
  .about-title span { display: block; }
  .about-title span + span {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--terracotta);
    font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 144, 'SOFT' 80, 'WONK' 1;
  }
  .page h2 {
    margin-block: var(--s-7) var(--s-3);
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 2.5vw, 2rem);
    letter-spacing: -0.015em;
    font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 144, 'SOFT' 80, 'WONK' 1;
  }
  .page .lead { font-size: 1.25rem; line-height: 1.5; color: var(--ink-soft); margin-bottom: var(--s-6); }
  .page p { margin-bottom: var(--s-4); }
  .page p em, .page li em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--terracotta);
    font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 16, 'WONK' 1;
  }
  .page ol { padding-left: 1.5em; }
  .page li { margin-bottom: var(--s-3); }
  .page a { color: var(--terracotta); border-bottom: 1px solid currentColor; }
  .about-cta {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: var(--s-3);
    margin-top: var(--s-8);
  }
  .about-cta .btn-ghost {
    display: inline-block;
    border: 1px solid var(--ink);
    color: var(--ink);
    padding: var(--s-3) var(--s-5);
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    transition: background var(--t-fast) var(--ease-out), color var(--t-fast) var(--ease-out);
  }
  .about-cta .btn-ghost:hover { background: var(--ink); color: var(--bg); border-color: var(--ink); }
  .about-cta .btn-jumbo {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--bg);
    padding: var(--s-3) var(--s-5);
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    border: 1px solid var(--ink);
    transition: background var(--t-fast) var(--ease-out);
  }
  .about-cta .btn-jumbo:hover { background: var(--terracotta); border-color: var(--terracotta); }
</style>
